Fire Fox, don't worry about it.

* Diana hissed and batted at the big reptile again, though she was 
frieghtened enough for her fur to turn white.
It was a futile attempt too, since she was tiny compaired to that big 
monster.
She spat at it before nearly jumping out of her pelt when Rion landed beside 
her, watching him skid near the creature and nearly scare her half to 
death.*

" About time!"

* She hissed at her friend while jumping forward and batting at the monster 
before pulling back.*
